Week 2: Mission "Wake Up the Army"

    The Core Rule: "Knights and Bishops must wake up before the Queen!"

    The Concept (Development): Your pieces are sleeping in the back row. You need to wake them up. Knights like to jump into the battle first, then Bishops. The Queen likes to sleep inâ€”don't wake her up too early, or the enemy will chase her!

    The Lab (Exercise):

        The Race to 4: Play a game. The first person to get both Knights and both Bishops off the back row wins the "Speed Badge" (even if they lose the game later!).

    Progress Check: Who should come out to play first: The powerful Queen or the jumping Knights?